Description: Vietnamese input method for Fcitx5
 GÃµ Nhanh is a modern Vietnamese input method addon for Fcitx5,
 featuring:
  * Fast and accurate Vietnamese typing
  * Support for multiple input methods (Telex, VNI)
  * Auto-tone correction
  * Smart word suggestions
  * Integration with GNOME, KDE, and other desktop environments
 .
 This package provides the Fcitx5 addon and CLI tools for managing
 Vietnamese input on Ubuntu and other Debian-based systems.
